#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.146"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.146-148:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.146-148:0.2"
msgid "11. Appamādapeyyālavagga"
msgstr "11. Abbreviated Texts on Diligence"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 146–​148. Candimādisutta → vatthasuttāni (bj) | vatthaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn45.146-148:0.3"
msgid "146–​148. Candimādisutta"
msgstr "146–148. The Moon, Etc."

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: candimappabhāya → candimāpabhāya (s1-3, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn45.146-148:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, yā kāci tārakarūpānaṃ pabhā, sabbā tā "
"candimappabhāya kalaṃ nāgghanti soḷasiṃ, candappabhā tāsaṃ aggamakkhāyati;"
msgstr ""
"“The radiance of all the stars is not worth a sixteenth part of the moon’s "
"radiance, so the moon’s radiance is said to be the best of them all. …”"

msgctxt "sn45.146-148:1.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.146-148:1.3"
msgid "aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.146-148:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, saradasamaye viddhe vigatavalāhake deve ādicco "
"nabhaṃ abbhussakkamāno sabbaṃ ākāsagataṃ tamagataṃ abhivihacca bhāsate ca "
"tapate ca virocati ca;"
msgstr ""
"“After the rainy season the sky is clear and cloudless. And when the sun "
"rises, it dispels all the darkness from the sky as it shines and glows and "
"radiates. …”"

msgctxt "sn45.146-148:2.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.146-148:2.3"
msgid "navamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.45"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.146-148:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, yāni kānici tantāvutānaṃ vatthānaṃ, kāsikavatthaṃ "
"tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati;"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, cloth from Kāsī is said to be the best kind of woven cloth. …”"

msgctxt "sn45.146-148:3.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, ye keci kusalā dhammā, sabbe te appamādamūlakā "
"appamādasamosaraṇā;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.146-148:3.3"
msgid "appamādo tesaṃ dhammānaṃ aggamakkhāyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.146-148:3.4"
msgid ""
"Appamattassetaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ "
"bhāvessati ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarissati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.146-148:3.5"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu appamatto ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti "
"ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.146-148:3.6"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ "
"nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti "
"vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.146-148:3.7"
msgid ""
"evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu appamatto ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti "
"ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarotī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.146-148:3.8"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.146-148:3.9"
msgid "(Yadapi tathāgataṃ, tadapi vitthāretabbaṃ.)"
msgstr "(These should all be expanded as in the section on the Realized One.)"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.146-148:3.10"
msgid "Appamādavaggo pañcamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.146-148:4.1"
msgid "Tathāgataṃ padaṃ kūṭaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.146-148:4.2"
msgid "mūlaṃ sāro ca vassikaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.146-148:4.3"
msgid "Rājā candimasūriyā ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.146-148:4.4"
msgid "vatthena dasamaṃ padaṃ."
msgstr ""
